## What it is

`__CLASS__` is a [Material 3 Expressive](https://m3.material.io/) TODO. Styles ship with the component (`styleUrls`); you do not need a separate global SCSS mixin.

## Import

```angular-ts name="app.ts"
import { __CLASS__ } from '@ngm-dev/mat-exp';

@Component({
  selector: 'app-root',
  imports: [__CLASS__],
  template: `
    <__SELECTOR_EL__ />
  `,
})
export class App {}
```

